content: It's good to go now and I recommend going when the weather is cool. There may be a little bugs in summer, but I recommend going from the end of May to the beginning of June.
If you visit the weather in the evening, the lighting is pretty and there are many photo spots.
had a great and memorable experience here~!
It's close to home and I go often. It's good to go with family friends and lovers and the photos come out really pretty.
Because it's beautiful and colorful, there are many attractions Because the light is very good, the photos are very good, and it's also good to leave beautiful photos.
The atmosphere is good and parking is easy. This is a place worth visiting at night. I like the cafe in the garden.
It's a great place to date in the evening. There is a cafe in the garden where you can take a walk while drinking coffee.
Gorgeous and beautiful ~ 9,000 won is not a waste. It's a great place for a date.
I was there day and night, but the night is definitely the best. Not big but well maintained.
It's a good choice to visit with family because it's in a rest area and there are many things to see~~
There are many things to see and it is good to play with children. But the food is a little small.
Beautiful place to enjoy colorful lighting with children. It's a place I want to go often.
The space is large and there are many shops. It's a great place to spend the night with your family.
The environment is clean and the light show is great. Unfortunately, the entrance fee is a bit expensive.
